<template>
  <biz-form :isEdit="true" :initInfo="info$" @submit-form="onSubmit">
    <template v-slot:courseRange="decorators">
      <add-course-un-limit-table
        :decorators="decorators.decorators"
        :initInfo="info$"
        @change="onCourseRange"
      ></add-course-un-limit-table>
    </template>
  </biz-form>
</template>

<script>
import BizForm from './component#/form'
import AddCourseUnLimitTable from './component#/add-course-unlimit-table'
import { EditUnlimitPackageService } from './edit-unlimit-package.service'
import { isEmpty } from 'lodash-es'

export default {
  name: 'EditUmLimitPackage',
  components: {
    BizForm,
    AddCourseUnLimitTable
  },
  serviceInject() {
    return {
      service: EditUnlimitPackageService
    }
  },
  rxState() {
    const { info$ } = this.service
    return {
      info$
    }
  },
  data() {
    return {
      reserveIsLimitInfo: {},
      validateCourseRange: ''
    }
  },
  methods: {
    onCourseRange(rangeCourse) {
      if (isEmpty(rangeCourse)) {
        this.validateCourseRange = '请选择课程范围'
        return
      } else {
        this.validateCourseRange = ''
      }
      this.rangeCourse = { ...rangeCourse }
    },
    onSubmit(form) {
      if (isEmpty(this.rangeCourse)) {
        this.validateCourseRange = '请选择课程范围'
        return
      }
      this.service
        .edit({
          id: this.info$.package_course_id,
          ...this.rangeCourse,
          ...form
        })
        .subscribe(res => {
          this.$router.push({
            name: 'brand-product-package-list'
          })
        })
    }
  },
  created() {
    // this.reserveIsLimitInfo = {
    //   reserve_is_limit: this.info$.reserve_is_limit,
    //   reserve_limit_day: this.info$.reserve_limit_day,
    //   reserve_limit_times: this.info$.reserve_limit_times
    // }
  }
}
</script>
